				<CHS>You have taught the Vrikolaks a harsh lesson. Unfortunately, you have also raised the attention of their legendary leader, the most feared Vrikolak, the Scarred Beast-King. He is returning from his exile to destroy you – so you must kill him first in a fierce duel.</CHS>
			</msgCompleted>
		</boss_hunt>
